 ssmen students share their real\, unfiltered experiences about choosing t
 heir majors and navigating their career journeys. Hear firsthand what the
 y wish they knew before declaring\, the challenges they faced\, and how t
 hey found their passions. Whether you're feeling undecided\, overwhelmed\
 , or just curious about different paths\, this event will give you insigh
 ts\, inspiration\, and practical advice to help you make informed decisio
