DESCRIPTION:Interested in working on campus this summer? Join the Office o
 f Residence Life to learn more about our available summer employment oppo
 rtunities. During this session\, we will provide an overview of several r
 oles\, including the Summer Resident Assistant\, Summer Central Office As
 sistant\, Summer Conference Desk Assistant\, and Summer Facilities Assist
 ant positions.\nAttendees will learn about the responsibilities of each r
 ole\, expectations for the summer term\, time commitments\, and the appli
 cation process. This session is a great opportunity to ask questions and 
 determine which position may be the best fit for you.\nWhether you are lo
 oking to gain leadership experience\, build professional skills\, or stay
  involved on campus over the summer\, we encourage you to attend.\nApplic
 ations for all summer positions are due Wednesday\, March 18\, 2026.\nCom
 muter students may attend but must be signed in by a resident following R
 esidence Life guest procedures.\n\nHosted by: Residence Life\n\nOnline Lo
 cation:  https://montclair.zoom.us/j/96981396737\n\nAdditional Informatio
 n can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12323282
