DESCRIPTION:In this workshop\, educators will learn how to leverage Genera
 tive AI to create custom GPTs that scaffold student learning and support 
 instructional goals. Through live demonstrations and guided practice\, pa
 rticipants will learn to create custom GPTs that support authentic assess
 ments\, such as role-plays and case studies. The workshop will emphasize 
 responsible and ethical AI use\, highlighting how thoughtfully designed c
 ustom GPTs can enhance student engagement\, support high-order thinking\,
  and enable authentic\, practice-based learning experiences. RSVP: https:
 //www.tickettailor.com/events/adpcenterforlearningtechnologies\n\nHosted 
