DESCRIPTION:Need help getting ready to register? Join us for a workshop th
 at breaks down the basics of course registration in a simple\, easy to fo
 llow way. We'll show you how to search for classes\, register for courses
 \, and figure out what to do if you run into issues like holds\, error me
 ssages or classes being full. Whether this is your first time registering
