DESCRIPTION:Build your career in Higher Education   \nWhether you're alrea
 dy working in higher ed or looking to break into the field\, our flexible
  program is designed to meet you where you are - and help you go even fur
 ther.\nWe're hosting a virtual information session on March 19 at 6:00 PM
 . This is a no-pressure\, exploratory space to meet our team and determin
 e if our program fits your goals.\nOur coursework offers a broad focus on
