 7th floor of the university\, this evening will feature live music\, comp
 elling performances\, delicious cuisine\, a night to never forget. Open t
 o all students and their guests\, this is your chance to experience the b
 eauty\, rhythm\, and sensuality of Haiti’s heritage. Don’t miss it!\n \n\
 nHosted by: Haitian Student Association\n\nAdditional Information can be 
 found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12292276
