CATEGORIES:Athletics
DESCRIPTION:Brief Description: \nNever swam before? No problem! These less
 ons will give you the important foundational skills in swimming and help 
 you be more comfortable in the pool. Learn how to use proper breath contr
 ol\, float\, and swim with a kickboard. \nSkills Focus:\n\nBeing comforta
 ble in the water\nLearning how to float on your back and front\nLearning 
 how to kick off the wall with a kickboard\nIntroducing proper breath cont
 rol in the water\nLearning how to tread water\nLearn alternate kicks (Fro
 ggy Kick)\nBeing comfortable in the deep end \nIntroducing arms to your s
 trokes\n\nHow do I Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a 
 valid Montclair State ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nMonday: 1-2PM & 5-6PM\nStu
 dent Recreation Center - Pool \n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAddit
 ional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engag
 e/event/11931654
DTEND:20260330T220000Z
DTSTAMP:20260317T163251Z
DTSTART:20260330T210000Z
LOCATION:Student Recreation Center - Pool
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Free Swim Lessons *Beginner*
UID:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11931654
URL:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11931654
X-HOSTS:Campus Recreation
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Montclair State University
CATEGORIES:Athletics
DESCRIPTION:Spring Strength Shadow! Welcome back to our annual Bench Press
  & Squat Competition. Come and test power and show your gains. Each event
  will feature 5 reps max. Whether you're chasing PRs or just want to flex
  for fun\, this event is for you! Bring your friends and your lifting str
 aps\, and see who can lift their way to the top prize!\nHow do I Sign-up?
 \n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a valid Montclair State ID\n\
 nWhen and Where?\n\nData: March 30th\nTime: 3pm - 6pm\nStudent Recreation
  Center\, Plae Room\n\nHow are results scored\n\nMaximum 5 repetitions \n
 1 attempt per lift after a warm up set\nScoring calculation: Weight lifte
 d x repetitions divided by body weight \nFinal score will be a total of b
 oth lifts combined \n\nPrizes: \n\nWill be given to the top 3 winners \nT
 ier 1:Beat Headphone\, Fitness Watch\, Air Fryer $100-$200\nTier 2: Massa
 ge Gun\, Meal Prep Kit\, Pilates Kit $50-$100\nTier 3: Foam Roller Set\, 
 Liquid IV\, Owala Water Bottle $20-$50\n\nFree T-shirts - limited supply 
 so show up early to claim one!\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditio
 nal Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/
 event/11933620
DTEND:20260330T220000Z
DTSTAMP:20260317T163251Z
DTSTART:20260330T190000Z
LOCATION:Student Recreation Center - Plae Room
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bench Press and Squat Competition
UID:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11933620
URL:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11933620
X-HOSTS:Campus Recreation
END:VEVENT
