DESCRIPTION:Throw it back to the days of glitter\, bright colors\, and the
  ultimate DIY era at 2010’s DIY Nostalgia Night! Recreate iconic favorite
 s like Galaxy Slime\, mixing shimmering glitter and bold hues for that cl
 assic space-vibe stretch. Build your own Galaxy Jar\, layering dreamy col
 ors and cotton clouds just like the crafts that once ruled YouTube. Then 
 jump into the fun of Finger Loom Bands\, making colorful bracelets just l
 ike the ones everyone traded and stacked in the early 2010s.\n \nHow do I
  sign-up?\n\nNo registration required\nFREE for students with a valid Mon
 tclair State ID\n\nWhere and when?\n\nTuesday\, April 7\n7pm-9pm\, must b
 e checked in by 8:30pm to participate\nStudent Recreation Center Lounge\n
 \n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Information can be found a
 t: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11965139
