DESCRIPTION:This workshop offers practical guidance on how to write a pers
 onal opinion in a clear\, organized\, and persuasive manner. Through simp
 le steps\, participants will explore how to formulate a thesis\, develop 
 solid arguments\, and support their ideas with examples. In addition\, th
 ey will work on the use of transition words and expressions to connect id
 eas coherently and fluently. Upon completion\, students will have concret
 e tools to express their opinions confidently and accurately in different
  academic contexts.\n\nHosted by: Center for Latino Heritage & Spanish La
