BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Montclair State University
CATEGORIES:Social
DESCRIPTION:Campus Recreation is hiring for the summer!\nWe want qualified
  staff to work during the summer at our 3 facilities on campus. \nNot cer
 tified? We can train you! \nIf you work full time\, we provide housing fo
 r free at the Village apartments!\nApply today\nApplications due by 4/10!
 \nAll employees must be current students\, registered for Fall 2026. Inco
 ming students can be hired starting July 1st. We offer part-time and full
 -time hours at both indoor and outdoor facilities. We will work around cl
 ass schedules\, but all staff must be able to work a minimum of 14 hours 
 (part-time)\, and 32 hours (full-time). Full time staff get free housing 
 at the Village.\nCurrently certified lifeguards - we accept all major cer
 tifications\, and can recertify you for free. \nNon-certified students - 
 Students that are not currently certified can take a pretest for free\, b
 efore you register for a lifeguard training course. If you pass the prete
 st\, and can work a minimum of 14 hours per week for the summer (average)
 \, than we will certify you for free. If you can work full-time\, we may 
 also be able to offer free housing for the summer (space is limited\, so 
 this option is first-come\, first-serve).\nSwim tests will take place bet
 ween March 23rd and April 10th\, 2026. \n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n
 \nOnline Location: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfHzsT63Iw7RF
 XdEgnhieKQJ4g0wKmeDIkIEgxcAhoToq77rg/viewform?usp=dialog\n\nAdditional In
 formation can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/
 12293368
DTEND:20260410T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260317T163251Z
DTSTART:20260410T160000Z
LOCATION:Online
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Summer Lifeguard Hiring
